{"type":null,"faqId":13068,"title":"H30-L01&H30-L02 手机自动关机或重启，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>手机自动关机或重启，若是可拆卸电池，可能是由于电池接触不良造成。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>请取下电池后，使用棉布蘸取酒精擦拭电池和手机上的触点，重装电池后开机。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>若问题依然存在，长按电源键打开选项菜单，选择<b>重新启动</b>。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若无法打开选项菜单，请长按电源键</span><span>6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">秒左右强制关机后开机，或长按电源键</span><span>13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">秒以上强制重启，或重装电池后开机。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>若重启后仍然出现问题，可能是由于某些第三方应用程序不兼容。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>建议您备份重要数据后将手机恢复出厂设置。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>若无法操作手机，请将手机强制升级。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进入</span> <span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn\">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，根据手机型号下载软件升级包，参考软件升级包中的升级指导操作。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>若问题依然存在，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>华为会定期在官网发布最新软件版本，以优化软件性能，请您及时升级软件，以体验更好的手机性能。</span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":3,"unUseful":8,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4018","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1401961298000,"seriesProductName":"H30-L01,H30-L02","visitedTimes":1121,"isUsefulFlag":null,